s/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係就會俾我搶走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：巴打"},{"pid":"971251bd04ef53de73c3ba72d8c982dc3f3e40dc","tid":42141,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"乜都就哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef8e7851c43bedd3c59bcf9b17ac9d839b0288a","tid":42141,"uid":11230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜都就哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一方對另一方太好係咪唔係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n會唔會令對方慢慢覺得好似大安旨意咁<br />\n<br />\n但諗番轉頭其實拍拖緊又就係要對對方好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都幾confused <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f555cf726d88c076022272ce5d08f951dfa4f6","tid":42141,"uid":37131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"明知佢岀去同fd玩到四五點先返屋企，一直唔訓等佢返黎攬住佢訓<br />\n<br />\n利申: 依家變成ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cab2a962cbcf2760f8cf8416f8a73ee7bc265d","tid":42141,"uid":18246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"有野唔開心都唔會同佢講因為佢會好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只會展露自己最正能量既一面氹佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fc0903841bbdf7cad4b8e07992040818c7bc93","tid":42141,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"<bl